@page "/"

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Contoso Identity Provider</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Contoso Identity Provider</h1>
        <p>
            Contoso Identity Provider is your gateway to secure, seamless, and efficient digital identity management.
            We empower businesses and individuals with state-of-the-art authentication and authorization services.
        </p>
        <h2>What is an Identity Provider?</h2>
        <p>
            An Identity Provider (IdP) is a system that creates, manages, and verifies digital identities.
            It ensures secure access to applications by authenticating users and granting appropriate permissions.
        </p>
        <h2>Benefits of an Identity Provider</h2>
        <p>
            - Enhanced security with multi-factor authentication (MFA) and single sign-on (SSO).<br>
            - Streamlined user experience across multiple platforms.<br>
            - Compliance with industry standards for data protection and privacy.<br>
            - Efficient identity lifecycle management for enterprises.
        </p>
        <h2>How Contoso Innovates</h2>
        <p>
            At Contoso, we leverage AI-driven security, blockchain-backed identity verification, and zero-trust architecture
            to redefine how digital identities are managed. Our innovative solutions ensure that your data remains safe while
            providing frictionless access to your digital world.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Join Contoso Identity Provider and experience the future of identity management!</strong></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
